      "content": "thanks. i guess i'm wondering about the \"intermittency\" thing you mentioned. some people say that even with better batteries, we basically can't hit net zero targets without a massive increase in nuclear because wind and solar just aren't enough on their own. do you think that's a fair assessment or is that just an exaggeration?",
